==Usage==
<nowiki>{{WTA|id=000000|name=yyy}}</nowiki> where 000000 is the code in the url of the site.

===How to spot the parameter "id"===
Consider the example for [[Mary Pierce]]. The URL for her profile is

<code><nowiki>http://www.wtatennis.com/page/Player/Info/0,,12781~</nowiki>'''6297'''<nowiki>,00.html</nowiki></code>

In this URL, '''''6297''''' serves as the id. So the syntax for the template would be

<nowiki>{{WTA|id=6297|name=Mary Pierce}}</nowiki>

